I '''Richard Stephen Dreyfuss''' (mibait Octubre 29, 1947) metung yang artistang Americanung pikabaluan dili uling king kayang pamaglage king pelikula, telebisyon ampng teatro manibat anyang tauling dake ning dekadang 1960s, kayabe no reng pelikulang ''[[American Graffiti]]'', ''[[Jaws (film)|Jaws]]'',  ''[[Close Encounters of the Third Kind]]'', ampong ''[[The Goodbye Girl]]''.

Sinambut yang [[Academy Award for Best Actor]] i Dreyfuss anyang 1977 para king ''[[The Goodbye Girl]]'', at mika nominasyun ya anyang 1995 para king ''[[Mr. Holland's Opus]]''. Sinambut ya mu namang [[Golden Globe Award for Best Actor – Motion Picture Drama|Golden Globe Award]], [[BAFTA Award for Best Actor|BAFTA Award]], at mika nominasyun ya anyang 2002 para king [[Screen Actors Guild Awards]] kareng kategoryang Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Drama Series and Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Television Movie or Miniseries.

